name: Spring Blossom Hair Clips
description:
This pair of clips would be lovely to complement spring/summer outfits. Made from satin in this seasons canary yellow. The flowers are mounted on crocodile clips and the flowers measure 3.5cm. If you would like something similar in a different colour, please do not hesitate to get in touch - I love making things to order.

These are delicate and if for a child will not withstand rough play

name: Girls Doll Hair Clips
description: Price is for one pair of handmade girlie mini doll hair clips. Doll measures approx 50mm head to toe. Each is secured to a 35mm crocodile clip for secure attachment to the hair. A lovely handmade accessory. Please choose either blonde or brunette.

name: Camellia Kanzashi Barette Salmon Pink - Red & Ivory also available
description: Beautiful Handmade Camellia Kanzashi Barette in Salmon Pink Satin.  The barette has one large flower and three leaf strands.  The flower has a gold braid centre.  The whole item measures 7cm wide by 13cm top to bottom.  The barette clip measures 4cm.  Ideal for weddings or other special occasions. I have a red and ivory version of this barette available at the same price and I also accept commissions. For more info visit www.kanzashi.co.uk

name: Japanese Blossom Kanzashi Barette
description: Stunning Handmade Japanese Blossom Kanzashi Barette.  The barette has one four double satin flowers in ivory and pink/red combinations.  Each flower has a diamante and stamens at its centre.  The whole item measures 10cm wide by 6cm top to bottom.  The barette clip measures 5cm.  Ideal for a gift, a treat for yourself or for weddings or other special occasions. I also accept commissions. For more info visit www.kanzashi.co.uk

name: Colourful Kanzashi Bobby Pins - pair
description:
Cute Handmade Kanzashi Bobby Pins available in four colours. Each Bobby pin has one flower measuring 3cm in diameter.  The flowers are made from authentic Japanese crepe and have a diamante and stamens at their centre. Price is per pair - please state colour when ordering - white - pink - blue or red.   I also accept commissions. For more info visit www.kanzashi.co.uk
